Overview

  This is a simple configuration if we would run the plugin using all the defaults.

Example

+---
<project>
...
  <build>
    <plugins>
	  <plugin>
	    <groupId>com.marklogic.maven</groupId>
	    <artifactId>maven-marklogic-plugin</artifactId>
	    <version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
	  </plugin>
    </plugins>
  </build>
...
</project>
+---
